'I hope not , O I hope not ! But it is better for me to stay there much better , much more dutiful , much happier . 
Please don't go with me , let me go by myself . 
Good bye , God bless you . 
Thank you , thank you . 
He felt that it was better to respect her entreaty , and did not move while her slight form went quickly away from him . 
