They began their perquisitions in Bleeding Heart Yard that same forenoon . 
Nothing had been done for the purposes of the pending investigation everything was in its genuine working dress , and in a certain honest rugged order . 
Three or four days of steady application tendered him master of all the facts it was essential to become acquainted with . 
Mr Meagles was at hand the whole time , always ready to illuminate any dim place with the bright little safety lamp belonging to the scales and scoop . 
Thus , when Daniel came back , he found the affair as good as concluded . 
