'Yes , said Doyce 'they are well . 
Daniel had an old workmanlike habit of carrying his pocket handkerchief in his hat . 
He took it out and wiped his forehead with it , slowly repeating , 'They are all well . 
Miss Minnie looking particularly well , I thought . 
'Any company at the cottage ? 'No , no company . 
