'O Fanny ! 'I tell you not to Fanny me , for I'll not submit to it ! I never knew such a thing . 
The way in which you are resolved and determined to disgrace us on all occasions , is really infamous . 
And you do know it does , and you do it because you know it does . 
The principal pleasure of your life is to remind your family of their misfortunes . 
And the next great pleasure of your existence is to keep low company . 
