But she was very pale . 
He had a lighted cigar in his hand , and brought with him airs of ale and tobacco smoke . 
'Pancks the gipsy , he observed out of breath , 'fortune telling . 
, and took such a pull at it , with his right eye shut up tight for the purpose , that he underwent a convulsion of shuddering and choking . 
