'I haven't been here half an hour . 
Eh , Miss Dorrit ? His little black eyes sparkled electrically . 
His very hair seemed to sparkle as he roughened it . 
He was in that highly charged state that one might have expected to draw sparks and snaps from him by presenting a knuckle to any part of his figure . 
'Capital company here , said Pancks . 
'Eh , Miss Dorrit ? She was half afraid of him , and irresolute what to say . 
He laughed , with a nod towards Clennam . 
'Don't mind him , Miss Dorrit . 
