'And my complaint is , pursued the lady , disregarding the low remark , 'that it is not the tone of Society , and that you ought to correct it , Mr Merdle . 
If you have any doubt of my judgment , ask even Edmund Sparkler . 
The door of the room had opened , and Mrs Merdle now surveyed the head of her son through her glass . 
