So , Tinkler the valet was instructed to find Miss Amy's maid , and to request that subordinate to inform Miss Amy that Mr Dorrit wished to see her in his own room . 
If Tinkler had happened to smile , however faintly and innocently , nothing would have persuaded Mr Dorrit , to the hour of his death , but that this was the case . 
As Tinkler happened , however , very fortunately for himself , to be of a serious and composed countenance , he escaped the secret danger that threatened him . 
