Dear Mr Clennam , it is possible that I have thought of you and others so much by day , that I have no thoughts left to wander round you by night . 
I cannot bear to turn my face further away from it . 
My heart is a little lightened when we turn towards it , even for a few miles , and with the knowledge that we are soon to turn away again . 
