There was no denying that the thing was a compliment to Mr Merdle , and was not a bad thing for Edmund if he liked it . 
It was just as well that he should have something to do , and it was just as well that he should have something for doing it . 
Whether it would be more agreeable to Edmund than the army , remained to be seen . 
