'Thank you , dearest Amy , returned Fanny , kissing her . 
Having embraced her Anchor with great affection , Fanny took a bottle of sweet toilette water from the table , and called to her maid for a fine handkerchief . 
She then dismissed that attendant for the night , and went on to be advised dabbing her eyes and forehead from time to time to cool them . 
, to make it very probable that I shall surprise you by what I am going to say . 
What I am going to say , my dear , is , that notwithstanding our property , we labour , socially speaking , under disadvantages . 
