Little Dorrit laid her hand upon the hand that held the bottle of sweet water , with a still more anxious look . 
Fanny , quite punishing her own forehead with the vehement dabs she now began to give it , fitfully went on . 
'That he has somehow or other , and how is of no consequence , attained a very good position , no one can deny . 
