I could make her seem older at once , by being myself so much younger . 
And I would be ! 'My dear sister , would you condemn yourself to an unhappy life for this ? 'It wouldn't be an unhappy life , Amy . 
It would be the life I am fitted for . 
Whether by disposition , or whether by circumstances , is no matter I am better fitted for such a life than for almost any other . 
There was something of a desolate tone in those words but , with a short proud laugh she took another walk , and after passing a great looking glass came to another stop . 
'Figure ! Figure , Amy ! Well . 
The woman has a good figure . 
I will give her her due , and not deny it . 
But is it so far beyond all others that it is altogether unapproachable ? Upon my word , I am not so sure of it . 
