Mr Sparkler , unable to resist the agonised cry from the depths of his country's soul , declared that he must go . 
It followed that the question was rendered pressing when , where , and how Mr Sparkler should be married to the foremost girl in all this world with no nonsense about her . 
Its solution , after some little mystery and secrecy , Miss Fanny herself announced to her sister . 
