The day came , and the She Wolf in the Capitol might have snarled with envy to see how the Island Savages contrived these things now a days . 
The choked old fountain , where erst the gladiators washed , might have leaped into life again to honour the ceremony . 
The Temple of Vesta might have sprung up anew from its ruins , expressly to lend its countenance to the occasion . 
Might have done but did not . 
Like sentient things even like the lords and ladies of creation sometimes might have done much , but did nothing . 
