And she is , no doubt . 
I am sensible of her being SO . 
'Who can be otherwise ? responded Mr Dorrit . 
Both in face and figure , she is quite uncommon . 
When the young people arrived last night , I was really surprised to see such charms . 
And he offered his hand . 
Mr Dorrit was enraptured by these attentions . 
