The searching look turned gradually to the floor , after taking Mr Flintwinch's face in its way . 
Mr Dorrit , discomfited by finding that he was the questioned instead of the questioner , applied himself to the reversal of that unexpected order of things . 
'I am ha a gentleman of property , at present residing in Italy with my family , my servants , and hum my rather large establishment . 
