Likewise that his extremely careless life has made him a very bad subject for it indeed . 
Mr Sparkler considered it a parallel case to that of some of our fellows in the West Indies with Yellow Jack . 
Mrs Sparkler closed her eyes again , and refused to have any consciousness of our fellows of the West Indies , or of Yellow Jack . 
'So , Amy , she pursued , when she reopened her eyelids , 'will require to be roused from the effects of many tedious and anxious weeks . 
And lastly , she will require to be roused from a low tendency which I know very well to be at the bottom of her heart . 
Don't ask me what it is , Edmund , because I must decline to tell you . 
'I am not going to , my dear , said Mr Sparkler . 
